text: Dallenwil is a municipality in the canton of Nidwalden in Switzerland. The main sights of Dallenwil are the ski and summer resort Wiesenberg/Wirzweli, the church St. Laurentius, and the pilgrimage chapel Wiesenberg. == References == == Other websites == * Dallenwil.ch official website Category:Municipalities of Nidwalden
title: Dallenwil
